Text.string: Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Hey there.
I'll kill you!||—Oh. Sorry, I was... talkin' to someone else!
Don't shoot! I mean, hey.
Please don't kill me! Uh...||—Sorry! Hi!
Good sunburn to you, Vault Hunter!
It's so damn hot—are you real?
Why is it still so HOT at night? My life is terrible!
Good evening, Vault Hunter.
Pandora was bad enough BEFORE the bandit clans united. Now it's a REAL crapfest.
The Calypsos don't seem to believe in much of anything. THAT'S what makes 'em so dangerous.
Rakks are good eatin'. A little stringy though. You gotta pressure boil 'em!
You have no idea how hard it is to find an honest job on Pandora.
Corporations may be self-serving greedy monsters—but besides the Crimson Raiders, they're the closest thing to a civilizing influence Pandora's ever had. Just saying.
On Pandora, we live off the scraps the corporations leave behind.
I actually had a nice little plot of land on Pandora before the COV took my home. They're using it for something called a... “livescream”?
Not everyone on Pandora's a bandit, y'know. Just... almost everyone.
I don't know what we'd do without the Crimson Raiders. Die, probably.
If you've ever seen a woman riding a fish out in the desert, then you just might have Pandoran fever!
Proud to say I've never resorted to cannibalism! Fingers don't count, right?
Pandora might actually be pretty nice without the endless hordes of bandits. And the skags. And the merciless sun. And the... nevermind.
I've NEVER eaten skag balls. On purpose.
I know a great recipe for sand-fried varkid legs. I should make 'em for you some time.
I don't know where the word Pandora came from, but I'm sure it means “neverending torture” in some alien language.
Where are the hot alien babes? I thought there would be hot alien babes in space. What a let down.
Can't get good varkid legs on this ship. It's a shame.
You Crimson Raiders got a pretty sweet ship right here.
Ellie did a damn good job fixin' up this ship.
Hell of a thing, a ship like this.
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawns]
[yawn] We are just blasting through naptime.
[yawn] Woo! All right.
[yawn] Whoa. Here we are.
I'll kill you!||—Eh, later.
Don't you turn your back on me.
Goodbye for now!
Crap, now I'm alone with my dumb thoughts.
What, no Pandora goodbye?
Whew! Now I can finally let one rip.
Later! Don't die!
If you die, can I have your kidneys?
Good luck out there!
This was the closest I've ever had to companionship and I'll treasure it always!
Thinking of getting myself some rakk leather shoes.
I could go for some skag milk right about now.
Yaaagahagh!||—Not quite right yet. Gotta practice!
The lost treasure of Azlan DeVega. Myth, or legend?
I. Am. Aliiiiiiive!
Something stinks.
I want my own ship sooooo bad.
I'm STARVING!
Damn you, Tyreen Calypso! Daaaaamn you!
Maybe it's time to switch up my facial hair situation.
Varkid roasted over a barrel fire sounds pretty good right about now.
I sure could go for some skag balls.
“Oh, yeah? Well at least I ain't no turd farmer!” That's what I should've said to that bastard. Next time, next time.
NO—DON'T EAT ME!||—It's okay. It was just a dream...
Well, I'm bored as hell. Maybe I should go shoot something.
All right!
Woo!
Hell yeah!
My man!
Go Vault Hunter!
Crimson Raiders all the way!
Let's do this! Yeah!
I see you! I see you!
All right! Here we go!
Yo! Let's go!
[burps]
[burps]

I'll be right here.
Just doin' me.

Don't forget me!
